    "body": "### Problem\r\n\r\nThere's no way of setting up system wide init.lua. I can set up sysinit.vim but there's no lua equivalent.\r\n\r\n### Expected behavior\r\n\r\nadd sysinit.lua recognition. Also would be fun if there was way to set up system wide ginit.vim and ginit.lua.",
    "closed_at": "2023-03-09T18:00:50Z",
