            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "ginit.vim and ginit.lua are intentionally not supported, what is the purpose of all these special cases? Just use autocmds or call functions from your main init.lua.\r\n\r\nsysinit.lua also is pretty questionable because you can just call a lua file from sysinit.vim. So it is not worth the extra complexity (though it's minor).",
